    "If the angle of minimum deviation is equal to angle of a prism for an equilateral prism, then the speed of light inside the prism is"
  ],
  "choices": [
    [
      "$3\\times10^{8}ms^{-1}$"
    ],
    [
      "$2\\sqrt{3}\\times10^{8}ms^{-1}$"
    ],
