      "$\\sqrt{3}\\times10^{8}ms^{-1}$"
    ],
    [
      "$\\frac{\\sqrt{3}}{2}\\times10^{8}ms^{-1}$"
    ]
  ],
  "correctAnswer": 1,
  "explanation": [
    "Equilateral prism $A = 60^{\\circ}$. Given $\\delta_m = A = 60^{\\circ}$.",
    "Refractive index $\\mu = \\frac{\\sin((A+\\delta_m)/2)}{\\sin(A/2)} = \\frac{\\sin(60)}{\\sin(30)} = \\sqrt{3}$.",
    "Speed $v = c/\\mu = \\frac{3\\times10^8}{\\sqrt{3}} = \\sqrt{3}\\times10^8 ms^{-1}$."
